data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!  Charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom Pool home.  The freshwater canal provides a beautiful private setting with abundant wildlife.  Completely renovated throughout.  Kitchen features granite countertops, wood cabinets, and pantry. The master bathroom leads out to the over-sized pool with a new pump and filter.  New roof November 2022, impact windows 2019, and newer AC.  Tile flooring throughout.  Public sewer and water.  The street has underground power lines providing additional protection from storms.  Storage areas located inside and out.  Furnishings are negotiable.  Conveniently located minutes to golf, shopping, restaurants, I-75, and a short drive to medical care and gulf beaches.
